reviews_data.review_text: I popped in to have an expresso, which was delicious! I left with a bag of coffee beans. I told the owner Flavio, that I had never had a Cannoli, he offered a fresh one.  He sure set the bar high!  It was so delicious!  Perfect texture and the flavor was amazing. I took one to a friend who said it was the best she had ever had.  Highly recommend stopping by while in Waxhaw.  Super convenient, outside seating great staff, truly an experience.  Thanks Flavio, great to meet you!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Keith - it was great to meet you and completely honored to have given you your first cannoli. Hopefully it won't be the last! See you back soon.

reviews_data.review_text:
My family and I came here on a Sunday morning. Boy oh boy am I glad we decided to stop for a coffee. We ended up with a pumpkin spice vanilla latte. A bomboloni. An Italian donut. A cannoli. 2 croissants. 2 cheesecakes. Here was our review!

My wife loved the Italian donut, my son and I did not love it so much. It’s more like a bread product rather than a donut. Wife came in at 4.5/5. My son came in at 3/5. I came in at 2.8/5

The bomboloni. WOW. Just wow. We all agreed 5/5. That coupled with the latte. What a way to start your Sunday. I’ve not had a donut like this. I had it stuffed with vanilla custard and it was not too sweet. Perfect amount of sweet level.

The cannoli. Let me preface this by saying our family doesn’t love cannolis. We got a cannoli and oh my good lord, it was AMAZING. A cooler cannoli filling with a fresh crispy crust. My son came in at 4.5/5 I came in at 4.9/5 and my wife came in at 4.5/5. (Again this is from a family of non cannoli eaters)

Chocolate croissant. Soft, warm, chocolate filled. We really enjoyed this one. 4.5/5 across the board.

We got full and haven’t tried the pumpkin cheesecake of the raspberry cheesecake yet, or the pistachio croissant.

My son gives holy cannoli 4.7/5. I give it 4.9/5 my wife gives 4.8! Definitely go enjoy some delicious treats and great coffee!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Frank - you made our day when we read this review! Very thoughtful and intentional, we appreciate all of this feedback. Hope to see all of you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Love it
Everything looked so good, tried the lemon bar and chocolate chip stuffed cannoli, delicious, can't wait to go back.

reviews_data.review_text: I love Holy Cannoli.  The staff is always so friendly and the coffee is so good. Love all the different options for sweet treats and love that they always have something new.  But you can never go wrong with the traditional cannolis. Best I have ever had!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Wow Dawn, thank you so much! We strive to create a friendly welcoming environment while you wait for your goodies, so glad you love our shop and hope to see you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: So disappointed to have gotten there today at 5pm only to find it closed.  Someone.has to update your Google hours. Now the BBQ will be disappointed. They were all waiting on Canolis.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Inessa, very sorry about causing the disappointment. This was a very recent change based on our staff's availability. Thanks for letting us know we need to make this change, it will be updated tonight. We hope you'll still consider us for your next BBQ!

reviews_data.review_text: Thank you for the amazing job on my daughter's birthday cake 🎂 Our guests enjoyed the cake and yummy pastries. It was all a hit.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Gabriela, we loved making this cake for your daughter, it was so fun! So happy to hear everyone loved it.

reviews_data.review_text: Very friendly worker and great selection of pastries. I ordered a plain bun with chocolate filling.

reviews_data.review_text: I heard great things about this place but was unfortunately disappointed. Our cheesecake was $17 for 2 slices…which would have been fine if it was good. It was not. The crust was soggy and the cheesecake had curds in it and tasted sour.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Olivia, we’re sorry to read about your experience, this is not in line with the standards we’ve set for our shop. Would you mind sending me an email at holycannoliwaxhaw@yahoo.com so I can get a few more details from you about your order and how we can make this right? Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: Holy Cannoli! I had a classic cannoli and latte here. They were delicious! The people were very nice too. They also had nice outdoor seating!

reviews_data.review_text: Authentic ? Cream puffs hardly filled with weird tasting cream. Rum baby's dry , no cream inside ! Eh, just not a good experience after spending 76.00 . Will wait to visit NY . Done with the so called Authentic pastry shops in Charlotte area.

Finally a New York cannoli in North Carolina! This was my second visit and the cannolis are outstanding! I'm from NY so I know cannolis. These are the best! Portions are large and prices are reasonable.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you Carol, and yes we agree that our cannoli rival some of the best NY bakeries! Glad you loved them, we work hard to maintain that authenticity. Hope to see you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Yum! Get the chocolate cannoli with cherry filling, you won't be disappointed!

reviews_data.review_text: Great experience ❤️

Delicious!!!☺️A wonderful stop, a wonderful experience. ☕️🍰🥐I can’t believe it took me so long to come here and I only live ten minutes away.
A lovely young lady named Addie, (her nickname, and yes she spells it this way) was   very polite, courteous, and such a pleasure to speak with. She never made me feel rushed even though I couldn’t decide which desserts to get.
So to the point ➡️ Perfect little store with one main dessert window so all of it is right in front of you. Everything is labeled, coffee menu is written out, get it and go.
The Specialty Coffee menu is amazing by the way. You will gaze upon a variety of Croissants, Gourmet Cookies, cakes and of course, Chocolate 🍫.
Killer cannolis and tiramisu
I would consider myself a cannoli connoisseur, and this is hands down the best cannoli I’ve ever had! Go for the classic! I will be back for that pistachio cake!

This spot NEVER disappoints. The Cannolis, chefs kiss! My wife and I also ordered this donut looking thing and the young lady offered to fill it with warm Nutella. I don’t care if it gave me diabetes, I will come back again for that mysterious delicious Italian creation!

DELICIOUS Italian desserts and coffee! The croissants are awesome, coffee is the best around and this pistachio cake - omg! Insanely good! The owner and staff are awesome too! This is a fantastic addition to Waxhaw; Stop by - you won’t be disappointed!

Who would have thought an Italian pastry shop in Waxhaw ??
Super friendly staff and great pastries
Sweetest workers and best deserts!! The coffee eclair was fantastic

I tried Holy Cannoli for the first time today. Two things are apparent: one, I don't know how to order coffee properly, and two, the cannolis here are to die for! My experience  here was a great one with the staff being very friendly. I will definitely be coming back here to try more of what's offered!
Very nice coffee

Stopped in to Holy Cannoli today for the first time, and wow! I wish I hadn't waited so long!! The ladies working were super sweet and patient, and the cannolis are AMAZING!!! Will definitely be back as soon as possible!

If you want some real quality desserts and are tired of the dime a dozen store bought junk foods you have to stop in here.

I tried 2 types of cannoli and some sort of Pistachio themed cake and both were exceptional with the cake being more particular to my tastes.

Good pricing and friendly, fast and fun service. Highly recommend. Right next to a local bookshop so grab something good, some coffee, and a book.
The cornetti allá crema remind me my youth

Darling little shop! Very friendly staff, extremely clean and tidy, nice selection of fresh Italian pastries. Stopped in for a latte to go while walking around the antique shops and will surely make that our custom when visiting Waxhaw!
Could have been in Italy.  Excellent.

Definitely not up to the hype.  Stale hard struffoli, soggy Cannoli shells $100,  Might try walking in and grabbing something fresh, but definitely won't order anything again.  Sorry, but the product needs to be better.
Glad to have a Cannoli store near me. I love cannolis, and these are great. Friendly staff, and quick service. A little expensive, but they're authentic and hand made, so it's worth it.
Authentic Italian sweets. Incredible cannolis
Authentic Italian cakes, cookies, and cannolis. Great service, great flavors. Highly recommend supporting this business.
Best Cannoli outside NY. Get down to Waxhaw and enjoy.
Wow.  You cant go wrong with any pastry.  Super fresh and top notch quality.  You wont be disappointed.  A must have if in or near Waxhaw.
Gorgeous works of art! These beauty's are as good as they look!
I've gone at least three times since they've opened and everytime the staff is nice and personable. The caramel lattè, connolis and crisoants are amazing and the baked goods are always fresh!!!

While craving a burger I ran across an Italian bakery and coffee shop and Waxhaw called Holy Canoli. As soon as you come through the door you're greeted by the smells of delicious pastries and a full case of goodies. I purchased two different cakes today and had the luxury of trying Italian rainbow cookies which was the first time I've ever tried them and I can tell you with confidence it will not be the last. Holy Cannoli Thank you. The warm hospitality and food was so good!

Amazing deserts, awesome service, and over wonderful experience. If you have not had the chance to check this place out then you must!

My friend and I had the fluffiest donuts stuffed with warm Nutella and it was perfection. Can’t wait to visit again.

Fresh -  great ingredients!
Finally some real Italian dessert in Waxhaw!
Authentic. Delicious. Love 💘
Possibly the best canoli I have ever had.  The Americano was also excellent.  Can't wait to go back and try everything else.
We visited on opening day and got three cannolis: chocolate, vanilla, and pistachio. All three were delicious and super fresh, but my favorite was the pistachio!

reviews_data.owner_answer: Frank - you made our day when we read this review! Very thoughtful and intentional, we appreciate all of this feedback. Hope to see all of you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Love it
Everything looked so good, tried the lemon bar and chocolate chip stuffed cannoli, delicious, can't wait to go back.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for this review Matthew, so happy that you loved your cannoli and lemon bar!

reviews_data.review_text: I love Holy Cannoli.  The staff is always so friendly and the coffee is so good. Love all the different options for sweet treats and love that they always have something new.  But you can never go wrong with the traditional cannolis. Best I have ever had!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Wow Dawn, thank you so much! We strive to create a friendly welcoming environment while you wait for your goodies, so glad you love our shop and hope to see you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: So disappointed to have gotten there today at 5pm only to find it closed.  Someone.has to update your Google hours. Now the BBQ will be disappointed. They were all waiting on Canolis.

reviews_data.review_text: Thank you for the amazing job on my daughter's birthday cake 🎂 Our guests enjoyed the cake and yummy pastries. It was all a hit.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Gabriela, we loved making this cake for your daughter, it was so fun! So happy to hear everyone loved it.

reviews_data.review_text: Very friendly worker and great selection of pastries. I ordered a plain bun with chocolate filling.
reviews_data.owner_answer: So kind of you to write this review, thank you so much!

reviews_data.review_text: I heard great things about this place but was unfortunately disappointed. Our cheesecake was $17 for 2 slices…which would have been fine if it was good. It was not. The crust was soggy and the cheesecake had curds in it and tasted sour.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Olivia, we’re sorry to read about your experience, this is not in line with the standards we’ve set for our shop. Would you mind sending me an email at holycannoliwaxhaw@yahoo.com so I can get a few more details from you about your order and how we can make this right? Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: Holy Cannoli! I had a classic cannoli and latte here. They were delicious! The people were very nice too. They also had nice outdoor seating!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you Ian! We worked hard to make a cozy place to sit outside, glad you noticed :) Hope to see you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Authentic ? Cream puffs hardly filled with weird tasting cream. Rum baby's dry , no cream inside ! Eh, just not a good experience after spending 76.00 . Will wait to visit NY . Done with the so called Authentic pastry shops in Charlotte area.

Finally a New York cannoli in North Carolina! This was my second visit and the cannolis are outstanding! I'm from NY so I know cannolis. These are the best! Portions are large and prices are reasonable.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you Carol, and yes we agree that our cannoli rival some of the best NY bakeries! Glad you loved them, we work hard to maintain that authenticity. Hope to see you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Yum! Get the chocolate cannoli with cherry filling, you won't be disappointed!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for these awesome photos of our shop Katie! And yes, chocolate and cherry is a classic combo for sure. Glad you loved it.

reviews_data.review_text: Great experience ❤️

Delicious!!!☺️A wonderful stop, a wonderful experience. ☕️🍰🥐I can’t believe it took me so long to come here and I only live ten minutes away.
A lovely young lady named Addie, (her nickname, and yes she spells it this way) was   very polite, courteous, and such a pleasure to speak with. She never made me feel rushed even though I couldn’t decide which desserts to get.
So to the point ➡️ Perfect little store with one main dessert window so all of it is right in front of you. Everything is labeled, coffee menu is written out, get it and go.
The Specialty Coffee menu is amazing by the way. You will gaze upon a variety of Croissants, Gourmet Cookies, cakes and of course, Chocolate 🍫.
Killer cannolis and tiramisu
I would consider myself a cannoli connoisseur, and this is hands down the best cannoli I’ve ever had! Go for the classic! I will be back for that pistachio cake!

This spot NEVER disappoints. The Cannolis, chefs kiss! My wife and I also ordered this donut looking thing and the young lady offered to fill it with warm Nutella. I don’t care if it gave me diabetes, I will come back again for that mysterious delicious Italian creation!

DELICIOUS Italian desserts and coffee! The croissants are awesome, coffee is the best around and this pistachio cake - omg! Insanely good! The owner and staff are awesome too! This is a fantastic addition to Waxhaw; Stop by - you won’t be disappointed!

Who would have thought an Italian pastry shop in Waxhaw ??
Super friendly staff and great pastries
Sweetest workers and best deserts!! The coffee eclair was fantastic

I tried Holy Cannoli for the first time today. Two things are apparent: one, I don't know how to order coffee properly, and two, the cannolis here are to die for! My experience  here was a great one with the staff being very friendly. I will definitely be coming back here to try more of what's offered!
Very nice coffee

Stopped in to Holy Cannoli today for the first time, and wow! I wish I hadn't waited so long!! The ladies working were super sweet and patient, and the cannolis are AMAZING!!! Will definitely be back as soon as possible!

If you want some real quality desserts and are tired of the dime a dozen store bought junk foods you have to stop in here.

I tried 2 types of cannoli and some sort of Pistachio themed cake and both were exceptional with the cake being more particular to my tastes.

Good pricing and friendly, fast and fun service. Highly recommend. Right next to a local bookshop so grab something good, some coffee, and a book.
The cornetti allá crema remind me my youth

Darling little shop! Very friendly staff, extremely clean and tidy, nice selection of fresh Italian pastries. Stopped in for a latte to go while walking around the antique shops and will surely make that our custom when visiting Waxhaw!
Could have been in Italy.  Excellent.

Definitely not up to the hype.  Stale hard struffoli, soggy Cannoli shells $100,  Might try walking in and grabbing something fresh, but definitely won't order anything again.  Sorry, but the product needs to be better.
Glad to have a Cannoli store near me. I love cannolis, and these are great. Friendly staff, and quick service. A little expensive, but they're authentic and hand made, so it's worth it.
Authentic Italian sweets. Incredible cannolis
Authentic Italian cakes, cookies, and cannolis. Great service, great flavors. Highly recommend supporting this business.
Best Cannoli outside NY. Get down to Waxhaw and enjoy.
Wow.  You cant go wrong with any pastry.  Super fresh and top notch quality.  You wont be disappointed.  A must have if in or near Waxhaw.
Gorgeous works of art! These beauty's are as good as they look!
I've gone at least three times since they've opened and everytime the staff is nice and personable. The caramel lattè, connolis and crisoants are amazing and the baked goods are always fresh!!!

While craving a burger I ran across an Italian bakery and coffee shop and Waxhaw called Holy Canoli. As soon as you come through the door you're greeted by the smells of delicious pastries and a full case of goodies. I purchased two different cakes today and had the luxury of trying Italian rainbow cookies which was the first time I've ever tried them and I can tell you with confidence it will not be the last. Holy Cannoli Thank you. The warm hospitality and food was so good!

Amazing deserts, awesome service, and over wonderful experience. If you have not had the chance to check this place out then you must!

My friend and I had the fluffiest donuts stuffed with warm Nutella and it was perfection. Can’t wait to visit again.

Fresh -  great ingredients!
Finally some real Italian dessert in Waxhaw!
Authentic. Delicious. Love 💘
Possibly the best canoli I have ever had.  The Americano was also excellent.  Can't wait to go back and try everything else.
We visited on opening day and got three cannolis: chocolate, vanilla, and pistachio. All three were delicious and super fresh, but my favorite was the pistachio!
